<div class="home">
  <div class="home-container">
    <div class="home-bio">
      <%= image_tag('gvr-profile-photo.jpg', class: "profile-photo") %>
    </div>
    <h1 class="greeting">Hi, I'm Gale.</h1>
    <div class="main-quote"><p>I'm a natural problem solver and a craftsman. My passion for combining great programming with stunning design brought me to Dev Bootcamp. I'm now seeking an opportunity to continue down my path of discovery and learning.</p></div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="home-solid">
  <div class="home-container">
    <div class="home-left">
      <h1 class="home-headline">A history of learning and building</h1>
      <ul>
        <ul>
          <h4>2014/2015 - Attended Dev Bootcamp to become a Full Stack Web Developer</h4>
          <li>MISSING label <span>- Cordova front end with a Rails-based API on the backend</span></li>
          <li>Lightning Vote <span>- Rails-based lightning talk management app</span></li>
          <li>GaleVanRossem.herokuapp.com <span>- Rails-based portfolio and blog site for myself</span></li>
          <li>Phasebook <span>- Rails-based social network for DBC students</span></li>
          <li>Rundeck <span>- Rails-based running time log</span></li>
        </ul>
        <ul>
          <h4>2013 - learned Javascript, Wordpress Development and e-commerce</h4>
          <li>DunkCityFL.com <span>- Custom theme Wordpress blog site</span></li>
          <li>Wrap-A-Tee.com <span>- I created and built an entire e-commerce business called Wrap-A-Tee.com.</span></li>
        </ul>
        <ul>
          <h4>2012 - learned HTML5, CSS3 and Adobe Edge Animate.</h4>
          <li>MadisensMatch.com <span>- I re-built the Flash animations in Edge Animate.</span></li>
          <li>EvolveFantasyFootball.com <span>- I learned how to build a site in Joomla and created a Kickstarter campaign.</span></li>
        </ul>
        <ul>
          <h4>2011 - learned Adobe Dreamweaver and Flash</h4>
          <li>MadisensMatch.com</li>
          <li>Kiwanis5krun.com</li>
        </ul>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="home-right">
      <%= image_tag('web-projects-alt.png', class: "home-page-image") %>
    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div>
    <div class="center-div">    
        <%= link_to "View Web Portfolio", web_portfolio_page_path, class: "button" %> 
    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="home-transparent">
  <div class="home-container">
    <div class="home-right">
      <h1 class="home-headline">Visual Design and Photography</h1>
      <p>I've been a photographer since I was three years old and I've always had an eye for images. It's not surprising that I eventually found my way to Graphic Design. My love of computers and the web ultimately led to Web Development.</p>
      <p>I've worked hard over the years to learn everything I could about visual communication, web design, programming, business and now web development. I think one of my greatest assets to any organization is the fact that I have a full understanding of both the creative process as well as the business logic on the back-end.</p>
      <p>I'm always looking for new ways to do things. I am always learning and always open to try new approaches.</p>
      
    </div>
    <div class="home-left">
      <%= image_tag('design-and-photography.png', class: "home-page-image") %>    
    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div>
    <div class="center-div">    
        <%= link_to "View Visual Portfolio", design_portfolio_page_path, class: "button" %> 
    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="home-solid">
  <div class="home-container">

    <div class="home-left">
      <h1 class="home-headline">Blog Post</h1>
      <%= link_to post_path(@post.id) do %>
          <h3><%= @post.title %></h3>
        <% end %> 
        <%= sanitize(truncate(@post.content, escape: false, length: 1200, separator: '</p>') { link_to "read more", post_path(@post.id) }) %>
    </div>

    <div class="home-right">
      <%= image_tag @post.image.url(:medium).to_s, class: "feature-blog-image" %>
      <div class="center-div">    
          <%= link_to "Read Blog Post", post_path(@post.id), class: "button" %> 
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div>   
  </div>
</div>
<div class="left-gutter home-page-fix">
  <div class="bio">
    <div class="profile-photo-wrapper">
      <%= image_tag('gvr-profile-photo.jpg', class: "profile-photo") %>
    </div>
    <div class="contact-button-wrapper">
      <div class="center-div contact-button">    
          <%= link_to "Contact", "mailto:galeforcevr@gmail.com:?subject=Gale's Portfolio site&body=Hi Gale, I was just taking a look at your website...", class: "button" %> 
      </div>
      <div class="social-button-bio"><a href="/connect"><%= image_tag('social-button.png') %></a></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="footer-spacer"></div>